minetest: Minetest (An InfiniMiner/Minecraft inspired game.)
minetest:
minetest: Minetest is an infinite-world block sandbox game and a game engine,
minetest: inspired by InfiniMiner, Minecraft and the like. It has been in
minetest: development and use since October 2010.
minetest:
minetest: Minetest is technically simple, stable and portable. It's lightweight
minetest: enough to run on fairly old hardware. It currently runs playably on a
minetest: laptop with Intel 945GM graphics. Though, as for the CPU, dualcore is
minetest: recommended.
minetest:
